snippet.title: Kingdoms of Amalur: Re-Reckoning - Collector's Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Kingdoms of Amalur: Re-Reckoning is coming to PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One September 8th, 2020.

The Collector’s Edition features:
- A highly-detailed Alyn Shir Figurine (20.8cm x 18cm x 14.2cm)
- A custom Amalur keychain
- Five pieces of original in-game artwork
- The award-winning game soundtrack composed by Grant Kirkhope
- A high-quality Collector’s Box 

SRP of $109.99/€109.99/£99.99.
----

Discord: https://discord.gg/amalur
